1
00:00:08,416 --> 00:00:13,375
♪

2
00:00:21,416 --> 00:00:24,333
♪ Here he comes,
here comes Speed Racer ♪

3
00:00:24,416 --> 00:00:27,750
♪ He's a demon on wheels ♪

4
00:00:27,833 --> 00:00:31,791
♪ He's a demon and he's gonna
be chasing after someone ♪

5
00:00:33,916 --> 00:00:36,875
♪ He's gaining on you
so you better look alive ♪

6
00:00:36,958 --> 00:00:40,166
♪ He's busy revving up
the powerful Mach 5 ♪

7
00:00:40,250 --> 00:00:42,500
♪ And when the odds
are against him ♪

8
00:00:42,583 --> 00:00:46,458
♪ And there's dangerous
work to do ♪

9
00:00:46,541 --> 00:00:52,333
♪ You bet your life Speed Racer
will see it through ♪

10
00:00:52,416 --> 00:00:55,375
♪ Go, Speed Racer
Go, Speed Racer ♪

11
00:00:55,458 --> 00:00:58,541
♪ Go, Speed Racer, go! ♪

12
00:00:58,625 --> 00:01:01,583
♪ He's off and flying as he
guns the car around the track ♪

13
00:01:01,666 --> 00:01:04,666
♪ He's jamming down the pedal
like he's never coming back ♪

14
00:01:04,750 --> 00:01:07,791
♪ Adventure's waiting
just ahead ♪

15
00:01:07,875 --> 00:01:10,875
♪ Go, Speed Racer
Go, Speed Racer ♪

16
00:01:10,958 --> 00:01:15,208
♪ Go, Speed Racer, go! ♪

17
00:01:23,416 --> 00:01:26,291
[ROBOT]
Melange is alive!

18
00:01:26,375 --> 00:01:27,583
[screams]

19
00:01:29,791 --> 00:01:31,250
[crashing]

20
00:01:36,708 --> 00:01:39,500
[ROBOT]
Melange is alive!

21
00:01:40,916 --> 00:01:42,666
[screams]

22
00:01:48,541 --> 00:01:49,875
[SPEED] Two racing
officials were attacked

23
00:01:49,958 --> 00:01:51,333
by a mysterious sports car

24
00:01:51,416 --> 00:01:54,500
and the police asked me to
help in the investigation.

25
00:01:54,583 --> 00:01:56,750
The mysterious car was
spotted and chased.

26
00:01:56,833 --> 00:01:58,125
[WOMAN screams]

27
00:02:06,541 --> 00:02:09,416
[signal ringing]

28
00:02:27,541 --> 00:02:29,000
[SPEED]
Huh?

29
00:02:29,083 --> 00:02:31,708
[SPEED] I found that a robot had
been driving the mystery car

30
00:02:31,791 --> 00:02:34,041
and a tape recording
of what the robot said

31
00:02:34,125 --> 00:02:35,833
gave us a valuable clue.

32
00:02:35,916 --> 00:02:39,833
It kept repeating the name
"Melange. Melange."

33
00:02:39,916 --> 00:02:42,291
Years ago, a race was
held at Danger Pass

34
00:02:42,375 --> 00:02:44,500
similar to the one
I was about to enter.

35
00:02:44,583 --> 00:02:47,375
Flash Marker, a builder
and driver of racing cars,

36
00:02:47,458 --> 00:02:49,125
was in the Danger Pass race.

37
00:02:49,208 --> 00:02:51,291
But he met with a
mysterious accident.

38
00:02:51,375 --> 00:02:55,833
The car he was driving
was called the "Melange."

39
00:02:55,916 --> 00:02:58,333
At the start of the new
race at Danger Pass,

40
00:02:58,416 --> 00:02:59,875
I was surprised to see a car

41
00:02:59,958 --> 00:03:02,500
which looked very much
like the old Melange

42
00:03:02,583 --> 00:03:04,166
with a pretty girl at the wheel.

43
00:03:04,250 --> 00:03:06,125
I had a feeling of danger.

44
00:03:19,916 --> 00:03:20,875
[gasps]

45
00:03:23,333 --> 00:03:24,291
[gasps]

46
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,458
[SPEED]
I recognized the pretty girl

47
00:03:28,541 --> 00:03:30,708
as Flash Marker's daughter,
Lilly, and realized the Melange

48
00:03:30,791 --> 00:03:32,916
was being driven
by remote control.

49
00:03:33,958 --> 00:03:35,500
[yells]

50
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:40,416
[screams]

51
00:03:43,541 --> 00:03:44,666
[FLASH JR.]
Ah!

52
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:47,458
He's one of the best
drivers I've ever seen.

53
00:03:51,291 --> 00:03:52,416
Now what?!

54
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:57,958
After I get revenge for my
father, I'll get rid of him.

55
00:04:01,291 --> 00:04:02,375
[ANNOUNCER]
The first group of racers

56
00:04:02,458 --> 00:04:05,166
has just passed
checkpoint number three.

57
00:04:05,250 --> 00:04:08,791
Car number 6 is in the lead,
followed closely by number 12,

58
00:04:08,875 --> 00:04:10,833
and the Three Rose Club car.

59
00:04:10,916 --> 00:04:15,250
Average speed right now
is 143.7 miles an hour.

60
00:04:15,333 --> 00:04:17,583
Take it easy, Pops, there's
nothin' you can do right now.

61
00:04:17,666 --> 00:04:19,708
The race still has
three more hours to go.

62
00:04:19,791 --> 00:04:21,166
[SPRITLE]
Three hours!

63
00:04:21,250 --> 00:04:23,166
How can I take it easy when
I'm worried about my son?

64
00:04:23,250 --> 00:04:25,125
I wanna know how
Speed's making out.

65
00:04:25,208 --> 00:04:26,458
[groans]

66
00:04:26,541 --> 00:04:28,875
Pops, put me down or I
won't have any breath left

67
00:04:28,958 --> 00:04:30,000
to cheer for Speed.

68
00:04:30,083 --> 00:04:31,625
[laughing]

69
00:04:31,708 --> 00:04:33,125
Better hang on to him, Pops,

70
00:04:33,208 --> 00:04:36,208
or he'll try to sneak a ride
in the trunk of the Mach 5.

71
00:04:36,291 --> 00:04:37,583
No wonder I feel tired;

72
00:04:37,666 --> 00:04:39,750
I've been hanging on
to you for an hour!

73
00:04:42,125 --> 00:04:44,958
I wonder where Trixie is.
Have you seen her Sparky, huh?

74
00:04:45,041 --> 00:04:47,708
Last time I saw her, she was
standing beside our car.

75
00:04:47,791 --> 00:04:49,416
Oh! I'll bet she's in it!

76
00:04:49,500 --> 00:04:50,708
[BOTH]
Huh?

77
00:05:04,083 --> 00:05:05,083
Ah...

78
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:12,291
[SPEED] Their car's too fast.
I can't overtake it.

79
00:05:12,375 --> 00:05:16,458
It's an amazing car and it might
be even better than the Mach 5.

80
00:05:16,541 --> 00:05:19,916
Some extra weight seems
to be holding me back.

81
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,458
I'd better check the trunk.

82
00:05:25,875 --> 00:05:28,125
Spritle, are you in there?
Come on out.

83
00:05:28,208 --> 00:05:28,666
[gasps]

84
00:05:28,750 --> 00:05:29,958
[TRIXIE giggles]

85
00:05:30,041 --> 00:05:33,166
I'm sorry, but Spritle's
not here, Speed.

86
00:05:33,250 --> 00:05:36,291
Trixie! Now what's the big idea?

87
00:05:36,375 --> 00:05:39,791
I wanna be in the race with
you, but not in the trunk.

88
00:05:39,875 --> 00:05:42,250
Spritle's welcome to
ride there all he wants.

89
00:05:42,333 --> 00:05:43,875
--[giggles]
--[SPEED] Is that so?

90
00:05:43,958 --> 00:05:45,500
Let me warn you, Trixie...

91
00:05:45,583 --> 00:05:48,083
No time, Speed.
We'd better get going!

92
00:05:48,166 --> 00:05:50,416
You're right as usual. Come on!

93
00:05:59,791 --> 00:06:01,291
Get ready!

94
00:06:01,375 --> 00:06:03,083
We'll start knocking some of
the other cars out of the race.

95
00:06:03,166 --> 00:06:04,541
Okay!

96
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:10,458
[screams]

97
00:06:10,541 --> 00:06:11,458
[chuckles]

98
00:06:11,541 --> 00:06:12,750
[yells]

99
00:06:14,666 --> 00:06:15,625
[yells]

100
00:06:18,333 --> 00:06:21,208
[DIVERS screaming]

101
00:06:25,125 --> 00:06:28,458
[CLUB DRIVER A]
This race is getting rough.

102
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:51,541
The Melange is such a great car
not even the Mach 5 can beat it.

103
00:06:51,625 --> 00:06:52,958
Huh?!

104
00:06:53,041 --> 00:06:55,000
The Three Rose Club cars...

105
00:06:55,083 --> 00:06:56,875
[growls]

106
00:07:06,250 --> 00:07:07,583
[FLASH JR.]
So this is it...

107
00:07:07,666 --> 00:07:09,708
I've already gotten rid
of Black and Green

108
00:07:09,791 --> 00:07:12,333
for what they did to
our father years ago...

109
00:07:12,416 --> 00:07:17,208
And now... now I'll get rid of
the rest of the Three Rose Team.

110
00:07:17,291 --> 00:07:19,625
Lilly. Can you hear me, Lilly?

111
00:07:19,708 --> 00:07:23,750
Lilly, wake up, it's Flash.
You'll be at Danger Pass soon.

112
00:07:23,833 --> 00:07:28,625
The time to avenge our father...
Lilly, we're going to get them.

113
00:07:28,708 --> 00:07:30,208
[FLASH JR. laughs]

114
00:07:37,666 --> 00:07:41,791
Look, not even the Mach 5
is fast enough to beat us.

115
00:07:41,875 --> 00:07:43,291
Yeah,

116
00:07:43,375 --> 00:07:44,791
but don't forget we've still
gotta go through Danger Pass

117
00:07:44,875 --> 00:07:45,666
and that'll be rough.

118
00:07:45,750 --> 00:07:47,083
As long as we stick together,

119
00:07:47,166 --> 00:07:48,583
we'll be able to take care
of the rest of the racers.

120
00:07:48,666 --> 00:07:50,375
You're right. We're
approaching Danger Pass now.

121
00:07:50,458 --> 00:07:52,791
And remember, do whatever
you have to to win.

122
00:08:12,833 --> 00:08:13,958
[BOTH gasp]

123
00:08:18,125 --> 00:08:19,666
I've seen that helicopter before

124
00:08:19,750 --> 00:08:22,750
when I was chasing that
mysterious sports car.

125
00:08:22,833 --> 00:08:24,500
You mean, it's more
than a coincidence?

126
00:08:24,583 --> 00:08:25,666
[SPEED]
That's what I mean.

127
00:08:25,750 --> 00:08:26,833
[TRIXIE]
I'll use the Homing Robot

128
00:08:26,916 --> 00:08:28,833
to call Inspector Detector.

129
00:08:28,916 --> 00:08:30,833
Car number 3 is
really the Melange,

130
00:08:30,916 --> 00:08:34,166
and it's being operated from the
helicopter by remote control.

131
00:08:34,250 --> 00:08:37,166
Lilly Marker is at the wheel.
She's in danger!

132
00:08:37,250 --> 00:08:40,125
We're approaching the Danger
Pass area; we need your help!

133
00:08:40,208 --> 00:08:41,291
[SPEED]
Go, Robot!

134
00:09:12,750 --> 00:09:14,583
Well, here we are
at Danger Pass,

135
00:09:14,666 --> 00:09:17,458
and now I'm gonna take care
of the Three Rose Team.

136
00:09:26,708 --> 00:09:27,666
[gasps]

137
00:09:29,208 --> 00:09:30,916
Oh, it says X3!

138
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,458
That's the Melange!

139
00:09:32,541 --> 00:09:34,625
Or its ghost, anyway!

140
00:09:39,666 --> 00:09:42,166
[FLASH JR.] Lilly. Lilly,
wake up. Now's the time!

141
00:09:42,250 --> 00:09:44,416
Now we can get revenge
for our father!

142
00:09:47,375 --> 00:09:49,333
[FLASH JR.]
Lilly, now's the time!

143
00:09:49,416 --> 00:09:52,500
No! Please don't
go through with it!

144
00:09:52,583 --> 00:09:53,916
I will.

145
00:09:59,916 --> 00:10:02,041
Hey, look out!
We're gonna crash!

146
00:10:03,291 --> 00:10:04,333
[yells]

147
00:10:05,666 --> 00:10:06,666
[screams]

148
00:10:06,750 --> 00:10:08,083
[tires screeching]

149
00:10:08,166 --> 00:10:09,541
[screams]

150
00:10:15,333 --> 00:10:16,875
[gasping]

151
00:10:22,375 --> 00:10:26,291
Oh, you've done
enough, Flash! Stop!

152
00:10:26,375 --> 00:10:28,416
I have two more to go, Lilly.

153
00:10:29,625 --> 00:10:31,500
Speed, we've gotta go faster!

154
00:10:46,458 --> 00:10:49,666
Ah... Two more to go, and
they're right down there.

155
00:10:53,916 --> 00:10:57,208
[crying]

156
00:10:59,916 --> 00:11:03,000
I'm sorry, I was just following
orders! I didn't mean to do it!

157
00:11:03,083 --> 00:11:04,958
Please don't smash into us!

158
00:11:05,041 --> 00:11:06,791
Oh, Flash, please
don't hurt them!

159
00:11:06,875 --> 00:11:08,541
You've done too much already!

160
00:11:12,666 --> 00:11:15,166
[yelling]

161
00:11:21,916 --> 00:11:24,625
I was too late. I've gotta
do something to stop it.

162
00:11:32,958 --> 00:11:34,375
This one'll be next.

163
00:11:38,166 --> 00:11:42,333
[whimpering]

164
00:11:43,541 --> 00:11:44,500
Huh?!

165
00:11:52,458 --> 00:11:53,416
[sighs]

166
00:12:01,125 --> 00:12:03,958
Huh...? How dare
they get in my way.

167
00:12:07,166 --> 00:12:08,125
[TRIXIE gasps]

168
00:12:10,291 --> 00:12:11,750
[LILLY groans]

169
00:12:14,750 --> 00:12:16,458
[whirring]

170
00:12:16,541 --> 00:12:17,541
[TRIXIE gasps]

171
00:12:20,541 --> 00:12:21,500
[SPEED]
Duck!

172
00:12:29,333 --> 00:12:30,416
[TRIXIE screams]

173
00:12:42,625 --> 00:12:44,125
[BOTH gasp]

174
00:13:11,125 --> 00:13:12,166
We've got to get out of here

175
00:13:12,250 --> 00:13:14,250
before all our
oxygen is used up.

176
00:13:14,333 --> 00:13:15,833
Let's try to climb out.

177
00:13:23,833 --> 00:13:26,208
[SPEED]
C'mon, gimme your hands.

178
00:13:26,291 --> 00:13:27,250
We're safe now.

179
00:13:27,333 --> 00:13:28,125
[FLASH JR.]
That's what you think!

180
00:13:28,208 --> 00:13:29,166
[BOTH gasp]

181
00:13:31,458 --> 00:13:33,916
I get rid of everybody
who gets in my way,

182
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,625
and that's what you did.

183
00:13:35,708 --> 00:13:39,083
Don't pull that trigger. The
police will be here any minute.

184
00:13:39,166 --> 00:13:40,666
[FLASH JR.]
That's what you say.

185
00:13:40,750 --> 00:13:42,416
It'll take them much longer
than that to get way up here,

186
00:13:42,500 --> 00:13:44,500
so here goes...

187
00:13:44,583 --> 00:13:48,000
Don't be scared. In only a few
seconds, it'll be all over.

188
00:13:48,083 --> 00:13:49,291
[SPEED]
I'm warning you! Don't!

189
00:13:49,375 --> 00:13:51,750
[FLASH JR.]
Oh yeah? [laughs]

190
00:13:51,833 --> 00:13:53,458
[SPEED]
You-You won't get away with it.

191
00:13:53,541 --> 00:13:54,375
[BOTH gasp]

192
00:13:54,458 --> 00:13:55,666
[LILLY]
No, Flash!

193
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:57,541
[FLASH JR. grunts]

194
00:13:57,625 --> 00:13:58,583
[yells]

195
00:14:08,666 --> 00:14:10,041
[BOTH gasp]

196
00:14:22,666 --> 00:14:24,666
[BOTH gasping]

197
00:14:26,625 --> 00:14:28,875
--[LILLY] Flash, where are you?!
--[TRIXIE] Speed! Speed!

198
00:14:31,625 --> 00:14:32,750
[BOTH gasp]

199
00:14:35,083 --> 00:14:37,125
That finishes him off for good.

200
00:14:40,708 --> 00:14:42,875
[FLASH JR.]
And our father is avenged.

201
00:14:44,458 --> 00:14:46,500
[LILLY]
Flash! I wanna talk to you!

202
00:14:46,583 --> 00:14:50,750
Flash! Wait, Flash, wait!
Don't leave me like this!

203
00:14:50,833 --> 00:14:52,208
Flash!

204
00:14:54,458 --> 00:14:56,416
Now for the race.
The Melange will win it.

205
00:14:56,500 --> 00:14:58,625
There'll be no more competition.

206
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:08,041
[SPEED groaning]

207
00:15:08,125 --> 00:15:11,166
Huh? Oh, Speed!

208
00:15:11,250 --> 00:15:13,333
Oh, look, he's been hurt!

209
00:15:14,833 --> 00:15:17,291
I'm going to get
the first aid kit!

210
00:15:18,958 --> 00:15:20,416
[LILLY]
He's in a state of shock,

211
00:15:20,500 --> 00:15:22,791
and if he isn't kept warm,
he won't pull through!

212
00:15:22,875 --> 00:15:25,791
I've got to save him
by keeping him warm.

213
00:15:25,875 --> 00:15:27,083
[gasps]

214
00:15:27,166 --> 00:15:29,291
[LILLY] I'm sorry for what
my brother Flash did

215
00:15:29,375 --> 00:15:31,541
to you and the others.

216
00:15:31,625 --> 00:15:32,666
[TRIXIE]
Get away!

217
00:15:36,375 --> 00:15:38,500
C'mon, Speed, you've
got to pull out of it.

218
00:15:38,583 --> 00:15:40,708
Speed, can't you hear me?

219
00:15:43,166 --> 00:15:44,291
You're all right.

220
00:15:44,375 --> 00:15:45,458
[SPEED]
Uh-huh...

221
00:15:55,875 --> 00:15:58,500
I never suspected Flash Marker
was behind this whole plot.

222
00:15:58,583 --> 00:16:02,500
It was clever of Speed to make
the discovery. He's a smart boy.

223
00:16:02,583 --> 00:16:05,375
Well after all, he's a chip
off the old block, Inspector.

224
00:16:05,458 --> 00:16:06,458
[POPS laughs]

225
00:16:06,541 --> 00:16:08,250
[POPS yelps]

226
00:16:08,333 --> 00:16:10,500
But most of the time, he has
more on the ball than you,

227
00:16:10,583 --> 00:16:11,708
right, Pops?

228
00:16:11,791 --> 00:16:14,041
Well, Sparky, I'm still
pretty sharp myself.

229
00:16:14,125 --> 00:16:17,708
[SPRITLE whimpers]

230
00:16:17,791 --> 00:16:19,083
Ah-choo!

231
00:16:19,166 --> 00:16:22,125
Oh? Spritle, you stowed
aboard again, huh?

232
00:16:22,208 --> 00:16:24,416
Right, Pops. Don't tell anybody.

233
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:28,958
[LILLY crying]

234
00:16:29,041 --> 00:16:31,541
I'm sorry. This all happened
because of my brother...

235
00:16:31,625 --> 00:16:33,916
[sobbing]

236
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,125
Stop crying, Lilly.

237
00:16:35,208 --> 00:16:36,541
You're not to blame
for the terrible things

238
00:16:36,625 --> 00:16:37,875
your brother did.

239
00:16:37,958 --> 00:16:40,291
He's old enough to answer
for his crimes himself.

240
00:16:40,375 --> 00:16:43,458
Right now, our problem is
what to do about the Mach 5.

241
00:16:43,541 --> 00:16:44,708
[LILLY]
I can't help it.

242
00:16:44,791 --> 00:16:46,041
Trixie's right.

243
00:16:46,125 --> 00:16:47,625
The important thing right
now is to get the Mach 5

244
00:16:47,708 --> 00:16:50,875
from under that snow bank
and catch up to the Melange.

245
00:16:50,958 --> 00:16:53,666
Okay, now stop feeling
so badly, Lilly.

246
00:16:53,750 --> 00:16:55,041
[LILLY sniffs]

247
00:16:55,125 --> 00:16:57,166
All right, Speed, thanks
for those kind words.

248
00:16:57,250 --> 00:16:59,166
Now, tell me what I
can do to be of help.

249
00:16:59,250 --> 00:17:02,083
Well, let's try to get the
Mach 5 out of the snow bank.

250
00:17:02,166 --> 00:17:04,958
We'd better hurry. Who knows
where the Melange is right now?

251
00:17:05,041 --> 00:17:07,125
Or what my brother
will try next.

252
00:17:14,625 --> 00:17:16,958
Ahh... Only one
more to get rid of.

253
00:17:17,041 --> 00:17:18,458
[growls]

254
00:17:59,750 --> 00:18:00,708
[gasps]

255
00:18:03,666 --> 00:18:05,166
The helicopter's up there!

256
00:18:05,250 --> 00:18:07,333
We must be near the
Melange. Hang on!

257
00:18:08,875 --> 00:18:10,291
[FLASH JR.]
Huh?

258
00:18:10,375 --> 00:18:11,833
The Mach 5 again...

259
00:18:11,916 --> 00:18:14,291
So I didn't get rid of
Speed Racer after all.

260
00:18:22,041 --> 00:18:24,208
[TRIXIE gasps]
There's the Melange!

261
00:18:24,291 --> 00:18:27,541
You'll have to drive the Mach 5,
Trixie! Now, don't be scared!

262
00:18:27,625 --> 00:18:29,083
[TRIXIE]
But I am!

263
00:18:29,166 --> 00:18:32,083
This is no time to act
like a girl, Trixie!

264
00:18:32,166 --> 00:18:33,500
Okay.

265
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:47,791
[SPEED] Now I've gotta find
where the remote control is.

266
00:18:47,875 --> 00:18:49,625
No sign of it over there...

267
00:18:49,708 --> 00:18:51,958
Well first I'd better find
out how the car works.

268
00:18:53,333 --> 00:18:55,208
This wheel doesn't work at all.

269
00:18:55,291 --> 00:18:56,375
[FLASH JR.]
Sorry, Speed,

270
00:18:56,458 --> 00:18:58,125
but the remote control
isn't in the car.

271
00:18:58,208 --> 00:19:00,416
I've got it up here
with me, of course.

272
00:19:01,875 --> 00:19:03,833
Now you'll be the driver
of the Melange, Speed!

273
00:19:03,916 --> 00:19:05,166
[laughs]

274
00:19:05,250 --> 00:19:06,166
[gasps]

275
00:19:06,250 --> 00:19:07,416
[laughing continues]

276
00:19:07,500 --> 00:19:10,125
Enjoy it, Speed.
It'll be your last ride.

277
00:19:17,875 --> 00:19:19,833
Watch out, Speed!

278
00:19:23,708 --> 00:19:25,875
[FLASH JR.] You don't have
much time left, Speed!

279
00:19:25,958 --> 00:19:28,416
[FLASH JR. laughs]

280
00:19:42,291 --> 00:19:45,125
[SPEED] I've got to keep my
head. I've got to stay calm.

281
00:19:46,166 --> 00:19:47,583
The center of that
remote control

282
00:19:47,666 --> 00:19:50,708
has got to be hidden in this
car somewhere. But where?

283
00:19:50,791 --> 00:19:52,208
I've got to find it.

284
00:19:56,708 --> 00:19:57,708
[SPEED]
A-ha!

285
00:20:00,333 --> 00:20:02,916
Careful, Speed. You're liable
to hurt yourself out there.

286
00:20:15,291 --> 00:20:17,625
[CLUB DRIVER C]
Huh?! The Melange is after me!

287
00:20:25,458 --> 00:20:26,958
[screams]

288
00:20:29,958 --> 00:20:31,458
[SPEED screams]

289
00:20:42,125 --> 00:20:45,916
Oh, the Melange! My father's
beautiful car has been wrecked!

290
00:20:53,541 --> 00:20:54,916
--[TRIXIE] Speed!
--[POPS] Speed!

291
00:20:55,000 --> 00:20:57,458
--[SPRITLE] Speed!
--Speed!

292
00:20:57,541 --> 00:20:59,083
Where are you, Speed?!

293
00:21:02,416 --> 00:21:04,375
[LILLY]
Ah!

294
00:21:04,458 --> 00:21:07,583
The Melange will never run
again. The Melange is finished!

295
00:21:07,666 --> 00:21:09,500
It was the most precious thing
my father ever owned!

296
00:21:09,583 --> 00:21:10,625
What have I done to it?!

297
00:21:10,708 --> 00:21:11,666
[gasps, screams]

298
00:21:13,375 --> 00:21:14,583
[shrieks]

299
00:21:20,333 --> 00:21:22,750
Flash! Oh, Flash!

300
00:21:24,125 --> 00:21:25,000
[SPRITLE]
Speed!

301
00:21:25,083 --> 00:21:26,958
[POPS]
Speed, where are you?!

302
00:21:27,041 --> 00:21:28,250
[TRIXIE]
Speed!

303
00:21:29,458 --> 00:21:31,083
[SPARKY] Nobody could've
survived this wreck...

304
00:21:31,166 --> 00:21:32,583
[DETECTOR] It's too bad
this had to happen...

305
00:21:32,666 --> 00:21:38,541
[SPRITLE wailing]

306
00:21:38,625 --> 00:21:40,041
I'm the one to blame
for losing Speed.

307
00:21:40,125 --> 00:21:41,583
I hope someday
you'll all forgive me,

308
00:21:41,666 --> 00:21:43,333
but the police had no
one else to turn to

309
00:21:43,416 --> 00:21:44,875
when we badly needed help.

310
00:21:44,958 --> 00:21:46,791
I should never've
asked him to do it.

311
00:21:46,875 --> 00:21:49,291
[POPS] I wish there
never been a Melange.

312
00:21:49,375 --> 00:21:52,041
Right now, I wish I'd
never heard of racing!

313
00:21:52,125 --> 00:21:58,083
[TRIXIE sobbing]

314
00:22:04,833 --> 00:22:06,041
Look, it's Speed!

315
00:22:06,125 --> 00:22:06,916
It's Speed!

316
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:09,291
C'mon, Speed!

317
00:22:09,375 --> 00:22:11,333
--[TRIXIE] Oh, Speed!
--[POPS] Speed!

318
00:22:12,833 --> 00:22:13,666
[TRIXIE, POPS, SPRITLE]
Speed!

319
00:22:13,750 --> 00:22:15,625
[POPS]
My boy!

320
00:22:15,708 --> 00:22:16,666
[BOTH]
Huh?!

321
00:22:20,625 --> 00:22:22,375
Glad you're safe, Speed.

322
00:22:22,458 --> 00:22:25,083
So are we all. We thought
you were done for.

323
00:22:25,166 --> 00:22:27,625
Aw, you knew I'd be okay.

324
00:22:27,708 --> 00:22:29,458
[POP, SPEED]
Oh...

325
00:22:38,666 --> 00:22:41,583
I remember when my brother was
little, he was such a good boy.

326
00:22:41,666 --> 00:22:43,375
It's too bad he had to change.

327
00:22:43,458 --> 00:22:45,041
Always remember him
when he was little

328
00:22:45,125 --> 00:22:47,291
and forget the way
he turned out.

329
00:22:47,375 --> 00:22:49,125
Now, we better go home, Lilly.

330
00:22:50,458 --> 00:22:52,000
I just want you to
know that Speed and I

331
00:22:52,083 --> 00:22:54,041
will always be your friends.

332
00:22:54,125 --> 00:22:55,416
Oh, will you?

333
00:22:55,500 --> 00:22:57,250
I'd like that more than
anything else in the world.

334
00:22:57,333 --> 00:22:58,458
And I hope that someday,

335
00:22:58,541 --> 00:23:00,750
you and everybody else
will forgive Flash.

336
00:23:13,708 --> 00:23:19,666
[KIDS laughing]

337
00:23:30,958 --> 00:23:32,208
[SPEED]
Are you hurt?

338
00:23:32,291 --> 00:23:33,666
[GIRL]
No, I like falling down.

339
00:23:33,750 --> 00:23:37,833
[ALL laugh]

340
00:23:37,916 --> 00:23:40,583
[NARRATOR] Speed has survived
the race at Danger Pass,

341
00:23:40,666 --> 00:23:44,333
but ahead lies even more
excitement... and danger.

